Package com.lugowoy.helper.filling.array.strings

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CharacterReader
    Functional interface for reading character data from a file into an array of char type.
    FillingArrayStrings
    This interface is the inheritor of the FillingArray interface and thereby redefines its contract for filling with object of the String type of an object of the Array wrapper class and an classical arrays.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FillerArrayStrings
    The class is the inheritor of the class FillerArray.
    FillingArrayRandomLengthValueStrings
    The class fills an object of the Array class and a classic array with random an object of the String type of the random length.
    FillingArrayRandomStrings
    This class implements the FillingArrayStrings interface by filling with object of the String type of an object of the Array wrapper class and an classical arrays.
    FillingArrayRandomValueStrings
    The class fills an object of the Array class and a classic array with random an object of the String type.
    FillingArrayReadingValueStrings
    The class provides functionality to reads data for fills an object of the Array class and classical arrays with object of the String type.
